## The Thought

Hiding bad news only makes the eventual impact worse. Be honest about progress.

## John’s Story

A dev admitted he was stuck on day 2. We paired him with a senior, and it was fixed by noon. If he'd waited until Friday, we'd have missed the Sprint.

## Today’s Challenge

Is there something you're afraid to tell your team or manager right now?
